title: Total solar eclipse 2030: Everything you need to know about totality in southern Africa and southeast Australia
description: The total solar eclipse on Nov. 25, 2030, will mainly cross the Indian Ocean, but views will be possible from Australia, South Africa, Namibia, Botswana and Lesotho.
